pageTitle: Itinerary for Wednesday, June 7, 2017 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Wednesday, June 7, 2017:

Ottawa, Ontario

10:00 a.m. The Prime Minister will attend the National Caucus meeting.

2:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will attend Question Period.

4:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will meet with Her Excellency Daw Aung San Suu Kyi, State Counsellor of the Republic of the Union of Myanmar.
